trans-unit.source: When used as a resource key for a data template, allows the data template to participate in the lookup process.
trans-unit.target: 當做為資料樣板的資源索引鍵使用時，允許資料樣板參與查詢處理序。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey.TemplateType" /> value that specifies the type of this template.
trans-unit.target: 指定這個樣板型別的 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey.TemplateType" /> 值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> class with the specified template type.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的樣板型別，初始化 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.target: 專為其設計此樣板的型別。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the assembly that contains the template definition.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定包含樣板定義的組件 (Assembly)。

trans-unit.source: The assembly in which the template is defined.
trans-unit.target: 其中定義樣板的組件。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type for which the template is designed.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定為其設計樣板的型別。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that specifies the type of object that the template is used to display, or a string that specifies the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] tag name for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] data that the template is used to display.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" />指定物件範本用來顯示，，或字串，指定的型別[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)]標記名稱[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)]資料範本用來顯示。

trans-unit.source: The object to compare for equality.
trans-unit.target: 要比較是否相等的物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether the given instance is identical to this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，指出特定的執行個體是否與 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> 的這個執行個體相同。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the two instances are identical; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果兩個執行個體相同則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.TemplateKey" /> 執行個體的雜湊程式碼。
